Magdalena Jasek is a Polish fashion model.
Career.
She started her career at the early age of 14 when he started shooting with Marilyn Agency. During her school years she only worked in Paris for haute couture shows. After she got her visa then she started doing international fashion weeks. She has walked for designers like Marc Jacobs, Alexander McQueen, Balenciaga, Louis Vuitton,Kenzo, Saint Laurent, Valentino, Maison Margiela, Giambattista Valli, Rag & Bone, Calvin Klein, Giorgio Armani, Givenchy, and Fendi.
